  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Say 'Aloha' to Hawaii!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kate and Nicole Robinson hit up Hawaii for a very special occassion: the wedding of their good friend Stella!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/ff0d06b67a162d8f0e30b3c9603ca1dc.poster.avif?t=1729490304\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/ff0d06b67a162d8f0e30b3c9603ca1dc.webm?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/ff0d06b67a162d8f0e30b3c9603ca1dc.mp4?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kate’s journey to Hawaii is more than just a vacation—she’s on a mission to help Stella have the most unforgettable wedding ever! Explore stunning Hawaiian locations, uncover hidden objects, and participate in fun mini-games that capture the spirit of the islands. Whether you’re discovering local secrets or helping with wedding preparations, every moment in Hawaii is a new adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/50d48300ed35a774e3120ee95b169246.poster.avif?t=1729490304\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/50d48300ed35a774e3120ee95b169246.webm?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/50d48300ed35a774e3120ee95b169246.mp4?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/8e99d78423cccdd4fa91e5591b63a0cb.poster.avif?t=1729490304\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/8e99d78423cccdd4fa91e5591b63a0cb.webm?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/8e99d78423cccdd4fa91e5591b63a0cb.mp4?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited Mode: Revisit your favorite Hawaiian spots anytime.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements: Unlock and showcase your progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Mini-Games: Enjoy a variety of tropical challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Downloadable Extras: Get wallpapers and the full soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hawaiian Fun Facts: Learn interesting trivia as you play.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/68f936a188e601e8bf98c36e3f6dc063.poster.avif?t=1729490304\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/68f936a188e601e8bf98c36e3f6dc063.webm?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/68f936a188e601e8bf98c36e3f6dc063.mp4?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/7b9a6a3b8ebd4d5f7e2e59601cfeb707.poster.avif?t=1729490304\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/7b9a6a3b8ebd4d5f7e2e59601cfeb707.webm?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107770/extras/7b9a6a3b8ebd4d5f7e2e59601cfeb707.mp4?t=1729490304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the handcrafted hidden object locations and immerse yourself in the natural beauty of Hawaii in First Time in Hawaii. Embark on this tropical journey and explore all that the islands have to offer.\"</p>",
